==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trapeze
<hw>Tra*peze"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>trap⟦egrave⟧ze</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Geom.)</fld> <def>A
trapezium. See <er>Trapezium</er>, 1.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A swinging horizontal bar, suspended at each end by
a rope; -- used by gymnasts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trapeziform</ent>⟦br⟧
